comments: Professor Sedwick is not the greatest lecturer, he mostly just does examples on the board that don\'t make too much sense. But some of the things stick with me and I actively think about them when working on a test or homework. Quizzes every week, they\'re quite easy, but tests are very difficult. That may just be thermodynamics, though.

Semester Project was a 30 page paper (written in a group). Gave oral exams (interesting set up) Also teaches some undergrad courses. Came from MIT. Reasonable guy. (seems like he would go out for a beer after class).
